  "title": "F&B Sales Executive | Class 3 | Redhill | 5 Days | Up To $3.3K - 4461",
  "description": "<p><strong>Sales Executive (F&B)</strong><br />Salary: Basic $3100 - $3300<br />Working days & hours: Mon - Fri | 9:45am - 6pm<br />Location: Redhill</p><p><strong>Job scopes:</strong></p><ul><li>Drive sales growth and manage key accounts.</li><li>Identify and unlock new business opportunities with smart strategies.</li><li>Build and maintain strong, lasting customer relationships.</li><li>Plan and execute sales campaigns to achieve targets.</li><li>Meet and exceed sales targets through proactive planning and execution.</li><li>Represent the company at events, trade shows, and client meetings.</li><li>Conduct market research to understand trends and customer needs.</li><li>Prepare sales reports and forecasts for management.</li><li>Collaborate with the marketing team on promotional activities.</li><li>Negotiate contracts and close deals to maximize revenue.</li><li>Monitor competitor activities and recommend strategic actions.</li><li>Provide excellent after-sales support to ensure customer satisfaction.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 3 years’ experience in food industry sales (selling to food producers is a plus)</li><li>Valid Class 3 driver’s license.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Email: supreme.jacksontan@gmail.com</strong></p><p><strong>Tan Yong Zhi (Jackson) | Reg: R24124461</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd | EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
